# generate all managed files
> managedFilesGenerate

# files exist with exact content and no banner
> checkExactNoBanner

# freshly generated files pass the up-to-date check
> managedFilesCheck

# tamper with one file...
> mutate

# ...and the check must fail
-> managedFilesCheck

# regenerating brings everything back up to date
> managedFilesGenerate
> managedFilesCheck

# a missing file must also count as out of date
> deleteOne
-> managedFilesCheck

# regenerating recreates it
> managedFilesGenerate
> managedFilesCheck
